Hi Amy,

>What does 100 feet look like?  How can I visualize 100 feet?

It's 1/3 of a football field.  

It's 16 average-height men lying head to toe.  

It's 10 times the height of a basketball rim. 

It's about the length of a blue whale.  

Does this help? 

